title: Cam Newton, Tua Tagovailoa, Rose Bowl, Rex Ryan, and the Patriots
itunes:title: Cam Newton, Tua Tagovailoa, Rose Bowl, Rex Ryan, and the Patriots
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb discusses Cam Newton still not being signed, Tua Tagovailoa appearing to be healthy, the 2006 Rose Bowl, Rex Ryan's comments about Amari Cooper, and the Patriots being hated by so many people. Guests include Geoff Schwartz, and Joel Klatt.
